spans.text: Their naked Tops the Hills admire , No longer white with fleecy Dew ; And as they moan the spreading Fire ,
Her Glebae still moist with fragrant Dews
Her Air still rich with balmy Gales
Thou Sacred Name , What Scenes Thy thoughtful Breast employ , Capacious as that mighty Frame You raise with Ease , with Ease destroy
the OLD , shall grace the NEW
